
# Paint with Simple Direct Layer (SDL)

## Tested Environments
- compiled and executed on Linux Mint
- SDL 1.2+

## Requirements
- SDL 1.2+ (http://www.libsdl.org)
- SDL_gfx (http://www.ferzkopp.net/joomla/content/view/19/14/)
- SDL_image (http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/)

## Debian, Ubuntu, Mint
- $ sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev
- $ sudo apt-get install libsdl-image1.2-dev
- $ sudo apt-get install libsdl-gfx1.2-dev

## Build
- $ ./make.sh
- or $ g++ -O3 `sdl-config --cflags` *.cpp -o sdlpaint `sdl-config --libs` -lSDL_gfx -lSDL_image
